Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下迷宫到底有多长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在其深处的秘宝又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 自称间谍的沙耶到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都尚不明朗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而现在 我却感觉和她在一起的这段时间弥足珍贵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不是见过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…从很久前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就喜欢沙耶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底 是从什么时候起喜欢上她的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到地下5层了 台阶应该就在附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 你看什么看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们随时可能袭击过来 而你却一点紧张感都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门外汉就是这么伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这样我们可能找得到秘宝…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可得怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,息怒息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它往下扯入口大概就会打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我们海拔不大够耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀借一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要骑上去 这还用问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 站起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树君 我跳上去扯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功咯!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来是尊石像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力VS力 正面交锋是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和那玩意交战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干倒它才能继续走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去找攻略法 附近应该有能让它停下的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不战谁战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 太危险了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是专业的 没那么容易挂掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只会碍事 闪一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个臭家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 我在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来会会你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明怕得都站不稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树君 把剑扔过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别废话 扔过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不扔我可发飙了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个少年痴呆!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭到脚了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是现在他们来袭 我们分分钟完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放放放我下来啦 我站得起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 当着淑女的面说人家重不觉得很没礼貌吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 丢脸丢到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,职业间谍落得个需要门外汉救的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太凄惨了 你干脆嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:07:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你负得起责任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家还是处女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸了处女就要负责的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一下爆出这么大的料我哪受得起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看应该没骨折
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 和你一起我总是不在状态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你这张笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 你最好别搪塞我 你刚才趁乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我…沙耶了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫沙耶桑也就算了 直接叫沙耶也太亲昵了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想叫你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什么时候 不过我觉得很久前也这么叫过你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个 理树君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大着胆子直说了 你别太吃惊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…喜欢理树君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…在战场上这种情况是可以有的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在觉得超受伤的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这股悲伤正慢慢转化成杀意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以毙了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 当然不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我死好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪你怪你怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不都怪你居然不肯对嘴儿!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不让我杀了你 要不让我自杀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想活在这种悲哀的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不是拒绝了你 只是吓了一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个大蠢蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这里是战场 接吻前也是要闭眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…那我就勉为其难了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何 我突然预感到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久后我或许会失去她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫叫看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 为啥那把剑正好出现在石像旁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得这迷宫有点戏弄入侵者的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我才没觉得害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,职业间谍是不会因为一个吻而动摇的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说我已经习惯接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其…其实那还是初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我可没说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就算脸红心跳也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怪叫什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是因为理树君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一脸只有我很在意的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 就当我的臀部身经百战好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是毫不在意我就难办了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就会突显出我非常在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也…很在意啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是初次和喜欢的女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生怎么能发出这种诡异的怪声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是你逼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 就算被逼也不会有人照做的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又…又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想你的时候跟你撞到一起我当然会吓一跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也怪我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得跟一对清纯情侣似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搅啊搅啊搅!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 你又来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得美少女不会做这种事对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作出羞耻发言后来个龌龊语句 这样就互相抵消啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会呢 女生不能说这种话的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵消不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不就只剩羞耻了吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧 有没受伤?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡…胡闹就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里就是最后难关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在不碰那玩意的前提下 通过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于抵达这最终决战之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终决战?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在抵达最底层的秘宝所在地前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须先在此和他一战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗之执行部的干部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是这个世界的最终BOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该就守在这前面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的黑暗仿佛在告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往前我就要和她永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 理树君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得藏在这地下迷宫里的秘宝是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说不是什么金银财宝 而是某种很革新的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UFO的动力引擎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 确实挺革新的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪美国和俄国都那么想要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 此话当真?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚 天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶觉得是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据我推测呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘宝是时间机器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要真是如此 比UFO厉害多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若非这种利器的话 就不会有间谍从世界各地被派来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间机器啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们得到了它 理树君想去什么时代呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 我想去一百年左右后的未来确认一下文化的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定百年后地球就毁灭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到未来就死掉 那就太蠢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是想回到过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可能的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回到小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后想重头来过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重头来过 再一次和理树君邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 假如…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说假如
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如这次任务顺利完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能邀你去约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊 就我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑幕在等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑幕?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像没资格这么说我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于现身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗之执行部 部长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时风 瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该夸赞你们 居然能来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 变得有模有样了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树君 不用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在叫我一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里必须由我出战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦 规则如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不守规则就找不到秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:18:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定…带你去约会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一句话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我消失!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次相恋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和理树君…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去…约会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我第几次死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,99次?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是更多?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我又开始等待理树君的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 原来是树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么晚还在校舍里逗留
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来取落下的笔记本…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别回头 跑到走廊尽头 从正面逃生门出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一放手你就跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的理树君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的搭档
